lead_paragraph: Red Bull's Daniel Ricciardo made it onto the podium at the Mexican Grand Prix on Sunday, but only after dark and with no sign of any other drivers.

headline.print_headline: No 'Shoey' but Ricciardo Gets His Podium in the End
